Price Reduced** Please submit your best offer by 12pm on Sunday January 28, no escalation clauses ** house have many new updates, new carpet in two rooms  and fresh paint. Welcome to this beautiful single-family home located in the heart of Davenport. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is perfect for those looking for a peaceful and comfortable living experience. The home features a spacious living room, a well-equipped kitchen with modern appliances, and a cozy dining area. The bedrooms are well-lit and offer ample space for relaxation. The property also boasts a large backyard that is perfect for hosting outdoor events or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine. Located in a quiet neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment options. Don’t miss out on this amazing opportunity to own your dream home.
